    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone looking for a solid foundation. The engine and transmission are fully functional, though you should expect some minor leaks and the typical wear that comes with its age. The exterior has several scratches and some fading paint, while the interior shows its use with some worn upholstery and minor electrical quirks. It is a dependable car that would benefit from a little TLC to bring it back to its former glory.",
