      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presented is a superlative specimen of the E46 M3, representing the pinnacle of the S54 inline-six platform. This vehicle features a meticulously maintained powertrain with a fully bulletproofed dual-VANOS system and recent rod bearing prophylaxis. The high-revving 3.2L engine delivers linear power through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, coupled with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. The chassis is structurally reinforced at the subframe mounting points\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and the suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers to maintain factory-plus handling characteristics. Every bushing is pliable, the cooling system is updated with a high-flow aluminum radiator, and the braking system utilizes floating rotors for optimal heat dissipation. This is a mechanically transparent, collector-grade example with zero deferred maintenance and a pristine undercarriage.",
      "price": 46500.0,
